title: Key players in trial of J. Alexander Kueng and Tou Thao, ex-cops charged in Floyd’s killing
dc:creator: Northwest Asian Weekly
description: Jury selection began Monday, Oct. 24, in the trial of two former Minneapolis police officers charged in George Floyd’s death. J. Alexander Kueng and Tou Thou are both charged with aiding and abetting second-degree unintentional murder and aiding and abetting second-degree manslaughter.
